&lt;h4&gt;Competitive Compensation and Benefits: Our educators earn competitive compensation based on level of education and experience. Full-time employees also receive benefits including tuition reimbursement, health, vision, and dental insurance, retirement savings, and commuter benefits.&lt;/h4&gt;
&lt;h4&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/h4&gt;
