&lt;p&gt;Vivvi is looking for passionate, experienced caregivers to deliver exceptional in-home backup care for one of its clients. While this role may look a bit different from a typical caregiving role, it is an exciting opportunity for someone who is flexible, and loves working with a variety of families!&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This is a guaranteed 40 hour per week position, meaning you will be paid for the time regardless if you are working. In this position you will be working with a variety of families on an as needed basis for urgent backup care needs (booked same day) or in advance between the hours of 7am - 6pm, Monday - Friday.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Included in employment package: PTO, health benefits, holidays&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We are seeking positive, flexible, patient and experienced caregivers who:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
